# ORIG TITLE    Amish sect leader jailed for hair and beard-cutting attacks . 
# ORIG CONTENT  Amish sect leader Samuel Mullet has been sentenced to 15 years for organising hair and beard cutting attacks against Amish people in Ohio in 2011. Amish people believe that the Bible instructs women not to cut their hair and for men to grow beards once married. The attacks were allegedly motivated by religious disputes. 
